Package: stm
Type: Package
Title: Estimation of the Structural Topic Model
Version: 1.1.4
Date: 2016-03-04
Author: Margaret E. Roberts, Brandon M. Stewart and Dustin Tingley
Maintainer: Brandon Stewart <bms4@princeton.edu>
